WEBVTT

00:12:28.513 --> 00:12:30.722
It doesn't matter whether I'm deaf

00:12:30.746 --> 00:12:32.523
or don't want to wake the baby.

00:12:32.547 --> 00:12:34.621
Both are equally valid.

00:12:34.985 --> 00:12:36.666
Smart designers

00:12:36.690 --> 00:12:40.413
include multiple ways
to access technology,

00:12:40.437 --> 00:12:46.049
but segregating that access
under "accessibility" --

00:12:46.073 --> 00:12:49.587
that's just hiding it
from mainstream users.

00:12:49.611 --> 00:12:52.547
In order to change how people think,

00:12:52.571 --> 00:12:54.377
we need to be more than accessible,

00:12:54.401 --> 00:12:56.762
we need to be connected.

00:12:56.786 --> 00:12:58.990
Apple did this recently.

00:12:59.014 --> 00:13:03.268
On my iPhone, it automatically
displays a visual transcript